IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User yevhenshymotiuk@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass Sites/Gmail/App/yevhenshymotiuk@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"[Gmail]/Important" !"[Gmail]/Starred" !"[Gmail]/Bin"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
